@page "/about"

<PageTitle>PickJSON - About</PageTitle>

<div class="page">

  <div class="w-full px-5 md:px-50 py-12 text-white overflow-y-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-light">About PickJSON</h1>
      <img src="pickjson.png" class="w-20 ml-10" />
    </div>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      <strong>PickJSON</strong> is a browser-based developer tool for converting JSON
      data structures into strongly typed source code.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      The site is intended for software developers who work with APIs and other
      forms of structured data.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      PickJSON is an independent project developed and maintained by an independent developer.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      The project was created to reduce repetitive boilerplate code and make working
      with JSON data easier.
    </p>

    <p class="leading-relaxed">
      For questions or feedback, you can contact us at
      <a href="mailto:pickjson@outlook.com" class="text-blue-300 underline hover:text-blue-500">
        pickjson@outlook.com
      </a>.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>